simpara
Element


simpara
&simpara.purpose;


&simpara.synopsis.gen;
Description



A SimPara is a simple paragraph, one that
may contain only character data and inline elements.  The
Para element is less restrictive; it may also
contain block level structures (lists, figures, and so on).


